{"tid":1569743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台禁播《願榮光》大家識做啦","createTime":"2019-09-14T17:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T17:45:07.000Z","uid":266736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"daaa2c8524dd337be37e628870907814652c972b","tid":1569743,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:25:29.000Z","msg":"邊個話唱歌無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190915&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60045476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190915%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60045476&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=6acb88c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190915%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60045476&h=1b8a5c1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190915&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60045476</a><br />\n<br />\n港台員工阿榮（化名）指，周五港台管理層與處長梁家榮開會後，<span style=\"color: red;\">改稱《願榮光歸香港》與港獨無關，但認為歌曲爭議大，不建議播放</span>，但無明言播放會否被秋後算賬。另有節目主持人指，監製未有強硬禁播，但就有「輕輕提醒」<span style=\"color: red;\">避免播放全首港人之歌</span>。"},{"pid":"162a587f5a485d07242c9ee985c7bef57e2c71ba","tid":1569743,"uid":266736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:28:37.000Z","msg":"聽日一路街一路唱"},{"pid":"26fc95c7fd31f3b48a9c5ab94a8e225adbcdcc4b","tid":1569743,"uid":264717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTpKA6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTpKA6q.jpg&h=bb039843&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AQJREL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AQJREL.jpg&h=5a9c28d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"250faa55c4bcddf9a9560ecba225e741d19f4ef3","tid":1569743,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T1